Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:02.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,這集絕對是福利回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是福利回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:07.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是給自己立了flag
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:11.28,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an2}{\1c&HA86C6F&}Re{\1c&HA9AB4B&}:{\1c&H7D60CC&}小{\1c&H4396E0&}劇場 {\1c&H000000&}其九
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:16.07,Petit,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}小{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}劇場{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}❾{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}西{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}瓜{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}攻略戰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:14.46,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣盯著我看 是有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:17.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 我只是在想 庫珥修的泳裝真帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:19.53,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:22.19,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這形容並不適用於泳裝打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:24.29,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,但直率又順耳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:27.85,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,直率又愛說正是昴君的魅力所在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:28.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:29.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆的泳裝打扮也是破壞力拔群
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:33.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,真是鬼上身了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.49,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼想娶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:39.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很可愛 但我沒說到那份上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:44.48,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,但如果不分對象地說出這種話會招致誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.91,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,請務必將對象只限於愛蜜莉雅大人和雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:49.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,真是順勢而為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.98,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,我在想卿們的感情真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:55.98,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,是的 感情非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:59.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,如此坦然地被這麼說 就算是事實我也會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.47,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,不過卿也是跟他們志氣相投的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,蛤！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼一說好像真的是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:07.73,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些 難得的機會 不來玩切西瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:10.26,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,為了能玩個盡興我帶了很多西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,雷姆小姐一如既往地值得信賴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:16.70,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,庫珥修 往右往右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:19.81,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,哼 這種謊話是騙不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:23.14,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,卿難道忘記了我的力量了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:25.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,難道在這個世界也有風視的加護
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:29.38,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,我就算被蒙著眼也能有點明白西瓜的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:30.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,和加護沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:39.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,等等你把第一次的當做沒發生了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.91,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 但雷姆不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:46.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,那個 雷姆小姐 雷姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.82,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,是的 昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:49.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,您手上拿的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:51.26,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,用來切西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,切西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:54.71,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,是的 用來切西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,砸了個稀巴爛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:00.72,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,砸了個稀巴爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你別突然出現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:06.10,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣就沒辦法賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,話說我還在想切好的西瓜去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是被你賣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:12.42,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 真是誣陷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:16.13,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,美女切開的西瓜只要100円什麼的我才沒幹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:19.25,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,從卿的話中看到謊言的風了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:23.23,Default,Anastasia,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是有看破謊言能力的賢才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:25.45,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,風視的加護 不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:30.42,SignA,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs10\bord5\pos(442,223)\an6\1c&H777777&\3c&H403D88&}美女切開的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:30.42,SignA,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\bord2\pos(442,240)\an4\1c&H267297&\3c&H000000&}西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:30.42,SignA,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs11\bord2\pos(467,255)\an4\1c&H506A53&\3c&H999999&}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:29.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,這和加護沒關係 是百分之百會暴露的謊言吧
